### Test Chat and Push Notifications

### 1. Update FCM Token
POST http://localhost:3001/api/user/fcm-token/USER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fcmToken": "YOUR_FCM_TOKEN_HERE"
}

### 2. Send Message
POST http://localhost:3001/api/messages
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "receiverId": "RECEIVER_ID_HERE",
  "content": "Hello! This is a test message."
}

### 3. Get Conversation
GET http://localhost:3001/api/messages/conversation/USER_ID_1/USER_ID_2
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 4. Mark Message as Read
PUT http://localhost:3001/api/messages/MESSAGE_ID_HERE/read
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 5. Mark All Messages as Read
PUT http://localhost:3001/api/messages/read-all/SENDER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 6. Get Unread Message Count
GET http://localhost:3001/api/messages/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 7. Get Recent Conversations
GET http://localhost:3001/api/messages/conversations
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 8. Create Helper Request (with notifications)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/helper/request
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "requesterId": "REQUESTER_ID_HERE",
  "requesterName": "Test User",
  "helperIds": ["HELPER_ID_1", "HELPER_ID_2"]
}

### 9. Respond to Helper Request (with notifications)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/helper/respond
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "helperId": "HELPER_ID_HERE",
  "requesterId": "REQUESTER_ID_HERE",
  "requestId": "REQUEST_ID_HERE",
  "accepted": true
}
